OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud and scattered
OL,6,Fshowers will move west this morning,
OL,7,Fgradually fading away. Sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping and feeling warm in this
OL,9,Fafternoon. Turning breezy for many,
OL,10,Fwith brisk winds along the south coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLow cloud will move into
OL,13,Fnortheast tonight. Staying dry with
OL,14,Fclear spells elsewhere and a patchy
OL,15,Frural frost. Windy in the southwest,
OL,16,Fparticularly around the coast and
OL,17,FMoors.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
