OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloud will linger along
OL,6,Fnortheast coasts on Wednesday. Plenty
OL,7,Fof sunshine for many and feeling warm.
OL,8,FHazy sunshine in the southwest with
OL,9,Fstrong winds and perhaps the odd
OL,10,Fafternoon shower.
